# BePlus Smart Search — plugin blocks

Standards: [`Document Plugin.md`](../../Document Plugin.md) § Gutenberg Blocks. Skills: `bpss-add-plugin-block`.

## Registration and build

- One folder per block under `blocks/` with `block.json`.
- `BlockRegistry` auto-discovers via `register_block_type_from_metadata()`.
- Built assets via wp-scripts → `build/blocks/` (or block-local `index.js` + `index.asset.php` if using custom pipeline).
- Extension filter: `beplus_smart_search.blocks`.

## block.json conventions

- `textdomain`: `beplus-smart-search`
- `category`: `beplus-smart-search`
- `name`: `beplus-smart-search/{slug}` (e.g. `beplus-smart-search/search-bar`)
- Prefer `render: file:./render.php` for dynamic search UI.
- Attributes: camelCase (`placeholder`, `showIcon`, `maxResults`, `enableLiveSearch`).

## Planned blocks

| Block | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `advanced-woo-search` | **Primary** — Woo filters (keyword, category, tag, attribute, stock); no page reload on shop |
| `search-bar` | Input + autocomplete dropdown |
| `search-results` | Full results list/grid; pagination |

Full build spec: [`docs/advanced-woo-search-block.md`](../../docs/advanced-woo-search-block.md).

## Editor and render

- `render.php`: escape output; use `get_block_wrapper_attributes()`; enqueue block styles via `block.json` `style` key.
- `block.js` / `edit` component: Inspector panels **Settings**, **Display**, **Behavior** — align labels with existing blocks.
- Live search: debounce input; call REST `GET /search`; show loading / empty / error states.
- Do not embed SQL or direct `WP_Query` in `render.php` for interactive search — use REST + JS or server render via `SearchEngine`.

## Styling

- Scoped classes: `beplus-smart-search__*` — inherit theme typography where possible.
- Loading state: `beplus-smart-search--loading` → `beplus-smart-search--ready` after init (avoid layout shift).
- Idempotent JS init: `data-bpss-search-init-pending` / `data-bpss-search-inited`.

## Reference

- GiftFlow block pattern: `plugins/giftflow/blocks/donation-button/block.json`
- Nextora spotlight search UX (theme): `themes/nextora-develop/blocks/spotlight-search/` — adapt combobox ARIA for plugin block

